Package no.uio.studentweb.sword

Interface Summary
TemplateUrlSourceData Interface to be implemented by the user of the module to provide access to data required by the Url templating code in EndpointDiscovery.
 

Class Summary
Constants  
Depositor Class to handle the deposit operations required between StudentWeb and the repository using SWORDv2.
EndpointDiscovery Main class for carrying out EndpointDiscovery operations The class should be constructed with all the relevant known information (see Constructor documentation), and then getEndpoints() can be called.
RepositoryItem Pseudo-entity object representing an item in the Repository.
 

Exception Summary
DiscoveryConfigurationException Exception class to be thrown when the EndpointDiscovery class finds itself being asked to carry out an action for which it has insufficient information
DiscoveryException Exception class which acts as the super-class for all exceptions thrown by this module.
NoServiceException Exeception class to be thrown when the EndpointDiscovery has been unable to acquire a service document url or a service document itself, for whatever reasons
TemplateUrlPropertyException Exception class to be thrown when the TemplateUrlSourceData implementation cannot interpret the property requested of it
